( No, only Gangon ran, where he got the idea that BB was running is beyond 
me, she never left the field.)

* BrightBlade swerved to the side and avoided Shredder's shot by a hair, she 
looked back at him and laughed.*

" Well, you obviously shoot as bad as you smell, Traitor!"

* She fired of a few shots at the boulder to let Shredder know that she 
didn't like him hiding like that...*

" Come out and fight, you coward!"

* She snarled as she ran up and jumped atop the boulder, she aimed her gun 
at the traitor's head and fired! She had to patience for traitors, none at 
all!!**
